396
00:35:06,320 --> 00:35:08,410
I'll introduce myself again.

397
00:35:08,410 --> 00:35:12,580
My Chinese name is Sheng Hanjun.

398
00:35:15,320 --> 00:35:17,520
Since you've come back,

399
00:35:17,520 --> 00:35:20,670
