402
00:35:31,800 --> 00:35:33,740
Did you know?

403
00:35:36,490 --> 00:35:39,480
During that fire,

404
00:35:39,480 --> 00:35:42,950
when I found your earrings,

405
00:35:42,950 --> 00:35:45,600
my heart died then.

406
00:35:48,290 --> 00:35:54,720
